data.description: Step into the inviting ambiance of 115 Kohler Mill Rd., where thoughtful design meets comfort. This charming bi-level residence, nestled on a corner lot in the Conewago Valley School District, boasts meticulous landscaping and a spacious garage, setting the stage for a warm welcome. Upon entry, be greeted by the airy elegance of vaulted ceilings in the living room, creating an immediate sense of openness and grandeur. The first floor seamlessly integrates functionality and style, featuring three cozy bedrooms and a well-appointed full bathroom. Transitioning effortlessly from indoor to outdoor living, a quaint balcony adjacent to the kitchen offers the perfect spot for alfresco entertaining. Ascend to the second level to discover a haven of relaxation and leisure, complete with a soaking tub in the second full bathroom and a versatile entertainment room that could easily transform into a fourth bedroom, catering to the dynamic needs of modern living. The fully finished basement presents an ideal retreat, with a convenient laundry room doubling as a practical mudroom entrance from the garage, enhancing the home's functionality with a touch of sophistication
